title: Saturday Night Live Season 15 Complete
description:
SNL Season 15 (1989-1990)

SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE SEASON 15 Starts WITH DANA CARVEY AS GEORGE BUSH TO PHIL HARTMAN AS PHIL DONAHUE DOING THE DONAHUE PROMOS. 

SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE BEGAN MAKING HEADLINES IN WHICH MIKE MEYERS & DANA CARVEY DOING THE WAYNE'S WORLD SKETCHES THROUGHOUT THIS SEASON. AND ON THE FEBRUARY 17th 1990 SHOW THE MUSICAL GUEST:AEROSMITH MADE A SPECIAL GUEST STAR IN THE WAYNE'S WORLD SKETCH. 

SO WITH OUT FURTHER ADO. HERE IS SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE The 15th SEASON!.

NOTE:SOME OF THE EPISODES ARE 1-HOUR EDITED VERSION THAT ORGINALLY SHOWN ON E!.

CONTAINNEY ONLY THE SELECTED SKETCHES AND 1 SONG FROM THE MUSICAL GUEST.
